  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Sausage Sports Club</strong> is a physics game about floppy animals playing sports!</h2><br>Play solo or couch co-op with up to 4 friends in <strong>Adventure Mode</strong>! Compete, make friends, and explore the toy-filled Overworld as you make your way through a season of the hit reality show <strong>Sausage Sports Club</strong>.<br><br>Having a party? Perfect! Up to 8 players can compete or play together in <strong>Free Play</strong>! Any way you play, you’ll unlock tons of customizations in characters, skins, and hats.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Sausage Sports Club</strong> is a physics game about floppy animals playing sports!</h2><br>Play solo or couch co-op with up to 4 friends in <strong>Adventure Mode</strong>! Compete, make friends, and explore the toy-filled Overworld as you make your way through a season of the hit reality show <strong>Sausage Sports Club</strong>.<br><br>Having a party? Perfect! Up to 8 players can compete or play together in <strong>Free Play</strong>! Any way you play, you’ll unlock tons of customizations in characters, skins, and hats.",
